[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      current procedure recovery, current treatment        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      course)                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Seam-flags registry                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Provenance metadata for every entry (source,         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    265[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      timestamp, ingestion path)                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient and caregiver preferences                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation history (initially empty)               │
