[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      relationship                                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Storage architecture]                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    272[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Structured state: DynamoDB tables with provenance    │
