[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    294[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      ServiceRequest, CarePlan, AllergyIntolerance,        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    295[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      Immunization)                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    296[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - HIE feeds and TEFCA QHIN integration where           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    297[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      participating                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    298[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Payer claims feeds (where the institution has a      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    299[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      claims-data partnership with the payer)              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    300[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pharmacy data via NCPDP standards or vendor APIs     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    301[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Home-health visit notes via vendor APIs              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    302[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scheduled-appointment feeds from connected           │
