[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    343[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      pharmacies, between clinicians, between              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    344[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      patient-reported and source-recorded)                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    345[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Referral non-scheduling detection (referral          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    346[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      ordered but not scheduled within protocol window)    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    347[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Transition-of-care incompleteness detection          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    348[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (post-discharge follow-up not scheduled within       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    349[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      protocol window; medication reconciliation not       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    350[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      completed; home-health orders not received by        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    351[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      receiving agency)                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    352[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Test-result acknowledgement gap detection (result    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    353[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      posted but not reviewed by ordering clinician        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    354[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      within protocol window)                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    355[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conflicting-order detection (two clinicians          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    356[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      ordering interacting medications without             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    357[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      coordination)                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    358[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-plan-item aging detection (item past expected   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    359[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      completion window)                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    360[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Lapsed-coverage detection (data source has gone      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    361[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      silent for an extended period)                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    362[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Confidence-flag generation for heuristic rules       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    363[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    364[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Protocol trigger evaluation]                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    365[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-plan-driven schedules (post-discharge           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    366[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      follow-up cadence, post-procedure recovery cadence,  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    367[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      treatment-course milestone cadence)                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    368[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Referral-lifecycle transitions                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    369[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Transition-of-care protocol initiation               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    370[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Medication-reconciliation protocol initiation        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    371[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient-and-caregiver-preferences-driven             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    372[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      adjustments                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    373[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
