[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    419[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Standard input safety primitives from recipe 11.1]     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    420[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Prompt-injection detection                           │
