[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    422[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Self-harm and crisis classifier                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    423[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    424[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Coordination-specific continuous emergency screening]  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    425[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Runs on every patient or caregiver utterance         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    426[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Detects acute-emergency presentations (chest pain,   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    427[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      severe shortness of breath, suspected stroke,        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    428[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      severe bleeding, suicidal intent)                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    429[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Detects high-acuity coordination events              │
