[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    431[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      reported missed medications affecting acute          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    432[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      conditions, reported caregiver crisis)               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    433[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Triggers immediate routing to triage (recipe 11.6),  │
