[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    435[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      institutional crisis line as appropriate             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    436[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    437[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Coordination-specific sensitive-disclosure detection]  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    438[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Caregiver-burden indicators                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    439[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Caregiver-abuse indicators (toward patient or        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    440[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      from patient)                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    441[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Elder-abuse indicators                               │
