[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    623[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Coordination-decision-record journal]                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    624[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Durable, separately-governed record of coordination  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    625[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      events (seam-flag detections and resolutions, care-  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    626[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      team alerts generated, escalations, protocol-driven  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    627[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      actions, patient-and-caregiver-reported context)     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    628[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Retention sized to the longer of HIPAA's six-year    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    629[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      minimum, state-specific medical-record retention,    │
