[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    639[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Coordination metrics (referral closure rate,         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    640[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      transition-of-care completion rate, medication-      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    641[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      reconciliation accuracy, seam-detection rate,        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    642[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      seam-resolution rate)                                │
