[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    644[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      patient-and-caregiver-reported satisfaction)         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    645[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-cohort metric slices (language, channel,         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    646[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      condition mix, age cohort, sex, social-determinant   │
