[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    655[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      provenance-gap, citation-gap, scope-violation)       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    656[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Protocol revisions driven by review findings with    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    657[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      clinical-leadership sign-off                         │
